					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-463500#post-1425990</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-463500/scp-1965#post-1425990</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 23 Apr 2012 18:36:26 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>ChazzK</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1203158</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Interesting&#8230; What I got from it was that human radio (and other) transmissions were what was causing the Silence. Little pockets here and there at first, and then growing more and more frequent and over wider areas, until our entire planet was blanketed in artificial signals 24/7. Which it is. And these poor beings that exist in some fashion we can barely comprehend were pushed more and more into the background, either irrevocably cut off from one another or outright wiped from existence, and this one alone was able to build up a &quot;loud enough voice&quot; to push through our noise.</p> <p>Also, I was able to thoroughly envision that collapsed broadcast in Freeman's voice, and it gave me *chills.*</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
