					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-463500#post-1425963</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-463500/scp-1965#post-1425963</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 23 Apr 2012 18:20:42 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Khym Chanur</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>163438</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>So, what is the &quot;Silence&quot; that prevents these things from communicating? Since it happened before humans began making radio transmissions, I'm guessing that these things came into existence shortly after the Big Bang, scattered across the universe, and when matter started to clump up the resulting gas clouds (and eventually dust clouds) blocked their radio waves.</p> 
				 	]]>
